dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"斯威士蘭19至49歲的人口中，超過四分之一對HIV呈陽性反應，是全球愛滋病問題最嚴重的國家。而當地所有愛滋病患者中，有83%同時患有肺結核。結核的死亡率為18%[11]。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2416e2ae04b3b2ed2517985844515cff6f23db06","tid":680063,"uid":185683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5442ce7e039a53d6b37466df70b65f8e0d791eb","tid":680063,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"人地要淘寶買黑仔唱生日歌嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff32b117aa167b18801354d955a1e125d70d3de9","tid":680063,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}